657
01:07:19,335 --> 01:07:20,495
Gosto, entendes?

658
01:07:24,473 --> 01:07:27,408
Sim, encanta-me.

659
01:07:28,344 --> 01:07:30,335
Sim, sim.

660
01:07:30,379 --> 01:07:32,370
Tenho uma teorpia agora,

661
01:07:32,381 --> 01:07:34,508
